main event: An unidentified flying object was observed over Elmendorf A.F.B., Alaska on 8 August 1952.
interesting points: The sighting was reported by a C.A.A. employee,The observation lasted for approximately 5 minutes,The object was reported to follow a greenish course,There was no noise associated with the sighting,The sighting involved 1 object at approximately 23 to 34 degrees above the eastern horizon.
